data.meta_description: Al Jarreau - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Al Jarreau was an American singer and musician who received 7 Grammy Awards over his career. He is known for his 1981 album "Breakin' Away" which included the hit "We're in This Love Together". He also sang the theme song for the 1980s TV show "Moonlighting". Jarreau performed with many jazz greats and had a successful career until announcing his retirement in 2017 due to exhaustion, and passed away just days later at age 76 from respiratory failure.
